    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/dfb40823923043cd73205e8eab6514ed.poster.avif?t=1756878236\" width=640 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/dfb40823923043cd73205e8eab6514ed.webm?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/dfb40823923043cd73205e8eab6514ed.mp4?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神秘的天坑“伤口”</h2>很久以前，为占领大陆爆发种族战争的时代，在战争开始不久后，大陆的中心出现了一个巨大的天坑。<br>这个因不明原因而产生的神秘天坑究竟隐藏着怎样的秘密？<br>和大陆上著名的探险队一起走进这个神秘的天坑，揭开它的秘密吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/d4e8af5e51612d491f5c7a10ab94d29b.poster.avif?t=1756878236\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/d4e8af5e51612d491f5c7a10ab94d29b.webm?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/d4e8af5e51612d491f5c7a10ab94d29b.mp4?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实时格子动作</h2>Guidus Zero是一款在战场上下左右移动，并进行战斗的实时格子动作类游戏。<br>仔细观察战场上敌人的位置和攻击范围吧。<br>瞄准正确的时机，避开敌人的所有攻击，挑战无伤通关吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/b888aee0962158635fc003f35723d3b6.poster.avif?t=1756878236\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/b888aee0962158635fc003f35723d3b6.webm?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/b888aee0962158635fc003f35723d3b6.mp4?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精灵之力和宝箱</h2>探索“伤口”时可以获得具有神秘力量的遗物，或者得到帮助你战斗的精灵祝福。与它们强强联手，发挥更强大的力量吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/53f6096b6d0c52c00e6f09b1f8ca2426.poster.avif?t=1756878236\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/53f6096b6d0c52c00e6f09b1f8ca2426.webm?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072640/extras/53f6096b6d0c52c00e6f09b1f8ca2426.mp4?t=1756878236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >被黑血侵蚀的敌人们</h2>从“伤口”最深处升起的黑色气息和被侵蚀的敌人在等着你。<br>击败各种敌人和强大的boss，到达“伤口”的最底层吧。<br>“伤口”的秘密和黑色气息的真相就在那里。",
